# PROMOTE.manifest -- what publishes from development to the public repo
# ===========================================================================
# Authority chain (single, canonical):
#     D:\code\ccode  (branch: development = source of truth, full history)
#         |  files matched below, minus .gitignore deny-list
#         v
#     C:\x64base     (branch: main = publication staging)
#         |  git commit + push
#         v
#     github.com/deraldg/x64base  (main = public snapshot; canonical for
#                                   downloads and pull requests)
#
# PURPOSE OF main: a PRODUCT DOWNLOAD for investigators -- the engine plus the
# HELP documentation, reader/user manuals, getting-started, sample data, and
# the scripts needed to build/run it. It is NOT a model/reference repo:
# metalevel "how we build it" material (doc engines, AI-/agent-facing docs,
# contracts, session/rationale docs, portal seeds, authoring aids) stays in
# development and is DELIBERATELY NOT PUBLISHED. See the NOT-PUBLISHED list
# at the bottom.
#
# This file is an ALLOW-LIST: of the clean files in development, only these
# publish. Everything else -- including most of docs/ -- stays private.
#
# FORMAT
#   - '#' begins a comment; blank lines ignored.
#   - Every other line is a path or glob, relative to the development root.
#   - '**' recurses; '**/' matches zero-or-more directory segments;
#     '*' stays within a path segment. Shell globbing.
#   - The rebuild re-applies .gitignore after matching (defense in depth).
# ===========================================================================


# ###########################################################################
# PUBLISHED -- the product (engine + help + samples)
# ###########################################################################

# --- entry + hygiene + license + public-repo health files ------------------
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.editorconfig
.github/workflows/*.yml
LICENSE
README.md
MANIFEST.txt
BUILDING.md
CHANGELOG.md
RELEASE_NOTES.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
SECURITY.md

# --- product launchers -----------------------------------------------------
dottalkpp/bin/*.bat
dottalkpp/bin/*.ps1
dottalkpp/bin/*.sh
dottalkpp/bin/*.ico
# NOTE: main currently carries BUILDING.md at docs/getting-started/BUILDING.md.
# Reconcile to ONE canonical location before the next promotion.

