# ###########################################################################
# PUBLISH LANE -- PYDOTTALK  (the Python server binding)
# ###########################################################################
# pydottalk is the Python server built from dottalkpp. Publish its full binding
# surface -- the C++ binding source, the Python API, build + starter, and the
# probe/smoke scripts. (__pycache__/*.pyc stay out via the .gitignore guard.)
bindings/**


# ###########################################################################
# NOT PUBLISHED -- stays in development (metalevel / dev environment)
# ###########################################################################
# Listed for clarity. These are simply ABSENT from the allow-list above; the
# lines below are commentary, not globs. If any are currently tracked in main,
# purge them (git rm --cached) -- they came from history, not from this list.
#
#   Metalevel docs:
#     AI_PORTAL.md  AI_README.md
#     docs/agents/**  docs/ai-friendly/**  docs/contracts/**
#     docs/maintenance/**  (rationale, lanes, session closeouts, build proofs)
#     docs/database/**  docs/planning/**  docs/ui/**  docs/diagrams/**
#   Manual AUTHORING aids + build assets (keep the rendered manual, not these):
#     DOTTALKPP_MANUAL_*.md  DOTTALKPP_PROFESSIONAL_*.md
#     docs/manuals/anchors/**  docs/manuals/assets/**
#     docs/manuals/command_reference/**  docs/manuals/dist/**
#     docs/manuals/developer/**   (developer manual + manualgen internals)
#   Documentation ENGINES + dev tooling:
#     tools/manualgen/**  tools/fullstack_docs/**  tools/gui_preview/**
#     tools/ci/**  tools/hygiene/**  tools/staging/**  dottalkpp/tools/help/**
#     PROMOTE.manifest  PROMOTION_*.md  (the promotion machinery itself)
#   Educational / portal:
#     labtalk/**   dottalkpp/docs/authority/**
#   ALPHA / separately-maintained subsystems:
#     pycrud/**              (ALPHA -- not ready to ship)
#     dottalk-webui/**       (the x64base-site -- maintained in its own pipeline)
#   Holdout products (outside the GitHub promotion path):
#     run-bible.ps1 biblerun.ps1 run-erp.ps1 erprun.ps1 artic*.datarun.*
#   Dev stress-test:
#     **/pinocchio/**   docs/maintenance/PINOCCHIO_*
#   Non-publish MDO content lanes (versioned in dev, never public):
#     **/messaging/**   **/metadata/**   **/sandbox/**
#   Never-version junk (also gitignored):
#     **/__pycache__/**  **/*.pyc  build*/  **/*.exe  **/*.lib  **/*.pdb
#     **/lmdb/**  **/*.cdx.d/
# ===========================================================================
